-- 2010-11-17T19:03:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-17/twins-gardenhire-padres-black-win-baseball-s-manager-of-the-year-honors.html
The Minnesota Twins’ Ron Gardenhire
was named American League Manager of the Year, while the San
Diego Padres’ Bud Black won the honor for the National League.  To contact the reporter on this story:
